title: Trading Places
description:
Mina and Mike Golic, Jr. discuss the haul the 49ers traded in order to move up to the 3rd pick in next month's draft, how Miami must really like a guy or a group of guys to move from 12 to 6, and what it means for the Eagles to trade down.
